Class Movie

  • java.lang.Object
    • assignment7.Movie
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Action, Comedy, Drama

    public class Movie
extends java.lang.Object
    Movie class stores the details of the movie Tracks the Motion Picture Association of America (MPAA) rating (e.g., Rated G, PG-13, R), ID Number, and movie title. Also, provides implementation method to calculateLate Fee
    Author:
    Animesh Jain
